item.title: Quotes
item.description: You’re not good enough yet, there’s a lot more work to do. -Unknown The things you think about determine the quality of your mind. Your soul takes on the color of your thoughts. -Marcus Aurelius Gratitude gives you power over adversity. -Unknown Comfort is the killer of man. -Unknown You can lead a horse to water but you can’t make it drink. -Unknown The world won’t lower its difficulty to cater to your weaknesses.
